{"name": "Uproar Church", "alternate_name": "", "description": "Need Help with Food? We're Here for You.

Life can sometimes throw unexpected obstacles our way—whether it’s job loss, fewer work hours, rising living expenses, or other personal struggles—that make it tough to put food on the table. That’s why, in collaboration with our non-profit partner UCARE, we provide free food assistance to individuals and families facing these difficulties.

If you could use this support, please reach out by emailing uproarcare@gmail.com. We will share more details as soon as we receive and review your message.

We look forward to serving you and your family.
